Built around the origin of hip-hop culture in America and adopting many of the east coast concepts, Party Naked will convert the venue & bring guests back to the Bronx of New York City by showcasing the 4 original elements of hip-hop music:

The Turntablist | The Emcee | Art | Dance

In addition to the 4 elements of hip-hop, guests will experience many other concepts that played a hand in building the culture. Fashion, basketball, tattooing, street musicians, barbery, and more! We cannot wait for everyone to experience Beat Street!

Want to get involved? For sponsorships and more information, contact Peter at peter@wepartynaked.com.
